{"tid":1382892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於食飯呢個問題","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:12:21.000Z","uid":1251,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0647fc041c264f529b20fc7932ceb02c763c7d94","tid":1382892,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"其實不如定期搞十七區慈善放映會<br />\n放映期間街坊可以自備食品飲品同其他街坊share<br />\n一來可以解決食飯問題<br />\n二來唔怕有狗陷阱，因為係街坊就黎得，大把人<br />\n三來又可以keep住士氣，一齊睇片屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n大家可以諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94935bc1ec26943a68f364ae9a7f84987cd55188","tid":1382892,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606ca528db950542a515384b2544419fe7ea312d","tid":1382892,"uid":249040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"［飯券義助］推到人道基金、文宣入黎！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩留言支持多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d1ec41e013f91c23fcc5ba8a395028fb69b3ff","tid":1382892,"uid":266766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73d3592fff899055ec566dc33506bbcfedba2cb3","tid":1382892,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692a8f256409f073e38d1197c58700f96b8fc637","tid":1382892,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019